  "id": "api/common/NgSwitch",
  "title": "NgSwitch",
  "contents": "\n\n<article>\n  <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/common/src/directives/ng_switch.ts?message=docs(common)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L35-L144\" aria-label=\"建议修改\" title=\"建议修改\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.1.0/packages/common/src/directives/ng_switch.ts#L35-L144\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n    <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n      {\n        \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n        \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n        \"itemListElement\": [\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/common\", \"name\": \"@angular/common\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/common/NgSwitch\", \"name\": \"NgSwitch\" } }\n        ]\n      }\n    </script>\n      <a href=\"/api\">API</a> / <a href=\"api/common\">@angular/common</a>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"ngswitch\">NgSwitch<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/NgSwitch#ngswitch\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label directive\">directive</label>\n    \n    \n    <label class=\"api-status-label stable\">稳定</label>\n    \n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n    \n  <p class=\"short-description\"></p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Adds / removes DOM sub-trees when the nest match expressions matches the switch expression.</p>\n<p translation-result=\"\">根据内嵌的 match（匹配）表达式（<code>match_express_*</code>）与 switch（多路开关）表达式（<code>switch_expression</code>）的匹配结果，添加 / 删除 DOM 子树。</p>\n<p></p>\n  \n\n  \n\n  <section class=\"directive-overview\">\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\">\n@<a href=\"api/core/Directive\" class=\"code-anchor\">Directive</a>({ selector: '[<a href=\"api/common/NgSwitch\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitch</a>]' })\nclass <a href=\"api/common/NgSwitch\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgSwitch</a> {\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/common/NgSwitch#ngSwitch\">set ngSwitch: any</a>\n}\n</code-example>\n</section>\n\n  \n\n  \n  \n<section class=\"selectors\">\n  <h2 id=\"selectors\">选择器<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/NgSwitch#selectors\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <code-example hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading selector\">\n  [<a href=\"api/common/NgSwitch\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitch</a>]\n  </code-example>\n</section>\n\n\n  \n<section class=\"inputs\">\n  <h2 id=\"输入参数\">输入参数<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/NgSwitch#输入参数\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  \n  <div class=\"input\">\n    <code><a href=\"api/common/NgSwitch\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitch</a></code> 绑定到 <code><a href=\"api/common/NgSwitch#ngSwitch\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgSwitch.ngSwitch</a></code>\n    \n  </div>\n  \n</section>\n\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">说明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/NgSwitch#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p translation-origin=\"off\"><code><a href=\"api/common/NgSwitch\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgSwitch</a></code> stamps out nested views when their match expression value matches the value of the\nswitch expression.</p>\n<p translation-result=\"\">当 <code>match</code> 表达式的值与 <code>switch</code> 表达式的值匹配时 <code><a href=\"api/common/NgSwitch\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgSwitch</a></code> 就会将其内嵌的视图 \"印\" 出来。</p>\n<p translation-origin=\"off\">In other words:</p>\n<p translation-result=\"\">换句话说：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p translation-origin=\"off\">you define a container element (where you place the directive with a switch expression on the\n<code>[<a href=\"api/common/NgSwitch\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitch</a>]=\"...\"</code> attribute)</p>\n<p translation-result=\"\">  你定义了一个容器元素（也就是你通过 <code>[<a href=\"api/common/NgSwitch\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitch</a>]=\"...\"</code> 属性来放置 <code>switch</code> 表达式的那个元素。</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-origin=\"off\">you define inner views inside the <code><a href=\"api/common/NgSwitch\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgSwitch</a></code> and place a <code>*<a href=\"api/common/NgSwitchCase\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitchCase</a></code> attribute on the view\nroot elements.</p>\n<p translation-result=\"\">  你在 <code><a href=\"api/common/NgSwitch\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgSwitch</a></code> 中定义了内嵌视图，并把 <code>*<a href=\"api/common/NgSwitchCase\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitchCase</a></code> 属性放在了视图的根元素上。</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p translation-origin=\"off\">Elements within <code><a href=\"api/common/NgSwitch\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgSwitch</a></code> but outside of a <code><a href=\"api/common/NgSwitchCase\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgSwitchCase</a></code> or <code><a href=\"api/common/NgSwitchDefault\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgSwitchDefault</a></code> directives will\nbe preserved at the location.</p>\n<p translation-result=\"\"><code><a href=\"api/common/NgSwitch\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgSwitch</a></code> 中位于 <code><a href=\"api/common/NgSwitchCase\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgSwitchCase</a></code> 或 <code><a href=\"api/common/NgSwitchDefault\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgSwitchDefault</a></code> 指令之外的那些元素会保留在原地。</p>\n<p translation-origin=\"off\">The <code><a href=\"api/common/NgSwitchCase\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitchCase</a></code> directive informs the parent <code><a href=\"api/common/NgSwitch\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgSwitch</a></code> of which view to display when the\nexpression is evaluated.\nWhen no matching expression is found on a <code><a href=\"api/common/NgSwitchCase\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitchCase</a></code> view, the <code><a href=\"api/common/NgSwitchDefault\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitchDefault</a></code> view is\nstamped out.</p>\n<p translation-result=\"\">在表达式求值完成之后，<code><a href=\"api/common/NgSwitchCase\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitchCase</a></code> 指令会告诉付指令 <code><a href=\"api/common/NgSwitch\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgSwitch</a></code> 要显示哪个视图。\n如果 <code><a href=\"api/common/NgSwitchCase\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitchCase</a></code> 中没有找到匹配的表达式，就会显示 <code><a href=\"api/common/NgSwitchDefault\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitchDefault</a></code> 视图。</p>\n\n</section>\n\n\n  \n\n\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n\n<section class=\"instance-properties\">\n  <h2 id=\"属性\">属性<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/NgSwitch#属性\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table property-table\">\n    <thead>\n      <tr>\n        <th>属性名</th>\n        <th>类型</th>\n        <th>说明</th>\n      </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n    \n      <tr class=\"instance-property\">\n        <td><a id=\"ngSwitch\"></a>ngSwitch</td>\n        <td><label class=\"property-type-label\"><code>any</code></label></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          \n          \n        </td>\n    </tr>\n    \n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</section>\n\n  \n\n\n  \n\n  \n<section class=\"usage-notes\">\n  <h2 id=\"usage-notes\">使用说明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/NgSwitch#usage-notes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <code-example>\n    &#x3C;container-element [<a href=\"api/common/NgSwitch\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitch</a>]=\"switch_expression\">\n      &#x3C;some-element *<a href=\"api/common/NgSwitchCase\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitchCase</a>=\"match_expression_1\">...&#x3C;/some-element>\n      &#x3C;some-element *<a href=\"api/common/NgSwitchCase\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitchCase</a>=\"match_expression_2\">...&#x3C;/some-element>\n      &#x3C;some-other-element *<a href=\"api/common/NgSwitchCase\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitchCase</a>=\"match_expression_3\">...&#x3C;/some-other-element>\n      &#x3C;ng-container *<a href=\"api/common/NgSwitchCase\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitchCase</a>=\"match_expression_3\">\n        &#x3C;!-- use <a href=\"api/router/RouterLinkWithHref\" class=\"code-anchor\">a</a> ng-container to <a href=\"api/animations/group\" class=\"code-anchor\">group</a> <a href=\"api/forms/SelectMultipleControlValueAccessor\" class=\"code-anchor\">multiple</a> root nodes -->\n        &#x3C;inner-element>&#x3C;/inner-element>\n        &#x3C;inner-other-element>&#x3C;/inner-other-element>\n      &#x3C;/ng-container>\n      &#x3C;some-element *<a href=\"api/common/NgSwitchDefault\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngSwitchDefault</a>>...&#x3C;/some-element>\n    &#x3C;/container-element>\n</code-example>\n\n</section>\n\n\n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/common\n - api/common/NgSwitchCase\n - api/common/NgSwitchDefault\n - guide/ajs-quick-reference\n - guide/cheatsheet\n - guide/dynamic-form\n - guide/structural-directives\n - guide/template-syntax\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/animations/group\n - api/common\n - api/common/NgSwitch#description\n - api/common/NgSwitch#ngSwitch\n - api/common/NgSwitch#ngswitch\n - api/common/NgSwitch#selectors\n - api/common/NgSwitch#usage-notes\n - api/common/NgSwitch#属性\n - api/common/NgSwitch#输入参数\n - api/common/NgSwitchCase\n - api/common/NgSwitchDefault\n - api/core/Directive\n - api/forms/SelectMultipleControlValueAccessor\n - api/router/RouterLinkWithHref\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/common/src/directives/ng_switch.ts?message=docs(common)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L35-L144\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.1.0/packages/common/src/directives/ng_switch.ts#L35-L144\n-->"
